# Allowlist for `podman build .` from the repo root, shared by every
# Dockerfile that takes the repo as its context (root Dockerfile +
# runner/Dockerfile today). Anything else in the build context is
# wasted bytes (and `terraform/.terraform` is a symlink pointing
# outside the repo, which trips podman's symlink check at context-
# load time). Pattern: exclude everything, then re-include the specific
# paths each COPY needs. Add new entries here whenever a Dockerfile
# gains a new COPY.
*
!mise.toml
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!packer
packer/*
!packer/qemu.pkr.hcl
!packer/aws/ami.pkr.hcl
!runner
runner/*
!runner/entrypoint.sh
